{"tid":560160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外判職員踢行李落樓梯　快運致歉","createTime":"2018-02-14T00:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T15:03:37.000Z","uid":121464,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"fa088bf11504b3940b2384422f8da700bc85f427","tid":560160,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180214/20305437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F20305437&d=FeJlmj9Q1x07v%2BLLY1cxfr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=756c51c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F20305437&h=8d7bc714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180214/20305437</a><br />\n<br />\n機場發生外判行李承辦商職員粗暴掟行李事件！前日下午2時許，目擊者莊先生在登機閘口看到在一班編號UO1844、由本港準備飛往日本大阪的航機，有職員疑在登機橋卸下多件行李時，竟然將行李沿樓梯高處拋下，行李應聲滾至地面，其間甚至用腳踢下行李。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n客運果邊應該係怡中 <br />\n<br />\n繼萬寧之後 Jardine又一醜聞 <br />\n<br />\n題外話 怡和係咪當所有為佢工作既低層員工都唔係人 出手又低 福利又少 機場地勤 零售相關新聞已經好多單"},{"pid":"e6de806a28d237ea5a29d71d044fa83359ea9633","tid":560160,"uid":997,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T00:22:40.000Z","msg":"道歉完之後咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70323d3466a6be48a22714c7a427fc0a852ad5bc","tid":560160,"uid":29314,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T00:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>道歉完之後咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你判上判請炒散，邊個會唔踢？"},{"pid":"a93c3c9c72f9b034912c5438ee5a11d4563692f1","tid":560160,"uid":629,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T00:25:02.000Z","msg":"淨係道歉有撚用 所以話永遠唔坐廉航"},{"pid":"ca82737e3990b445aa4f8058ac6f86882c96b5c6","tid":560160,"uid":102096,"like":2,"d